description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Stationary Bike Workout for Beginners | 20 Minute' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This ride is all about the saddle! If you're a beginner or just got a stationary bike or exercise bike, this 20 minute beginner stationary bike workout is for YOU!
